---
title: Mumbai Yoghurt Chicken with Roast Veggie & Spinach Toss
description: There’s nothing better than chicken that’s juicy on the inside and wonderfully charred with mild spices on the outside.
That’s how we’re preparing our low carb dinner tonight, plus add a dollop of creamy yoghurt to double down on all
that flavour.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
